  "text": "The PI3K/AKT/mTOR pathway, which is frequently deregulated in PCa [CITATION_1] was also investigated. In PC-3 Sh-PRMT6 cells, AKT, pAKT and mTOR protein expression was significantly decreased ( Figure 5B), suggesting PI3K/ AKT/mTOR pathway downregulation associated with PRMT6 silencing.",
